	Aniston retard    
	 Aug. 20: Actress Jennifer Aniston has come under fire for using the word retard in a TV interview, reports The Daily Telegraph.      
	Aniston, who was promoting her new movie The Switch on US chat show Live with Regis and Kelly, has been criticised by disability groups after using the word in reference to a recent photo shoot.       
	 reference to the Harpers Bazaar shoot, she replied to a question from co-host Regis Philbin by saying: Yes, I play dress up! I do it for a living, like a retard!    
	Bloom kid    
	Los Angeles (PTI): Actor Orlando Bloom and his model wife Miranda Kerr are expecting their first child. Kerr, 27, has confirmed that she is pregnant with Blooms child, People magazine reported. Yes, I am pregnant, said Kerr, confirming much buzz about a possible baby after the couple married in July.                                                                                                                                                       
